The function `addTitle` creates a styled on-screen title positioned at (1.3, -0.95) using specified font and alignment for displaying text consistently across the application's interface.

def addTitle(text):
    return OnscreenText(text=text, style=1, fg=(1, 1, 1, 1), font=font,
                        pos=(1.3, -0.95), align=TextNode.ARight, scale=.07)
